      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still logging in. everything just feels... heavy. the lab results came back today and it's another dead end. another year of work down the drain. i feel like i've spent my whole life building this one path and now it's just a cliff. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for something that doesn't want me back.",
