      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should reach out for help, but everything feels so performative. even talking about it feels like another task on a list i can't finish. it's like... the only way to actually get the silence i need, the real rest where nothing is expected of me, is to just stop everything. completely. i'm so tired of the struggle. i just want to find a way to finally be at peace and not have to worry about failing anymore.",
